{
  "stem": "18572.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember, though, that there was no basic language that all the kids could communicate.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So in order to-- even though we were learning Hebrew, you sort of needed another language to translate into, and I had no language.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had-- at this point, I spoke Polish and Russian.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I learned Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's when I learned Yiddish, was in Eschwege, because that was the sort of communal language.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then I learned Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I learned Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, it was just a regular day, where we learned all the different subjects.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But after school, it was very Zionistic, the whole camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And most of the people in the camp, or a certain-- most of the people in school that I remember belonged to two parties, the two opposites-- the Hashomer Hatzair and the Betar.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- we belonged to the Betar.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was the real, you know, right-wing Jabotinsky.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- [LAUGHS] I had a uniform-- that we went to all the meetings.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had marches for every-- every holiday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When the British executed some of the Irgun people, our-- our Betar kids all walked out of school on a march.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was, like, very, very militaristic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, we were being trained to be soldiers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, there was no two ways about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was very appealing to me, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think if you've been a victim for so long and been so scared, to think in terms that you're being trained to be a soldier and you're gonna go and fight for your fatherland was a very, very appealing thing to me.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember we were crawling on our bellies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, I was, like, eight years old-- that I'm crawling with a make-believe gun.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
